name: The Mystery v5-dv2 (chroma), (Eternity Render 3)
description: The Mystery v5-dv2 was created in 2021 for a show called "Sea Change" with Vellum LA / SuperRare. The Mystery v5 is a talisman in the style of Baroque memento mori. This is 3 in a series of 5 renders of this digital sculpture. This version is made of chromatic foil and posterpainted clay. PNG file, 2480 x 3508 pixels
